headline: Firing on All Cylinders: Church & Dwight (NYSE:CHD) Q1 Earnings Lead the Way
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how household products stocks fared in Q1, starting with Church & Dwight (NYSE:CHD).
